Security programs often miss it and it creates a number of Registry entries, which makes it difficult to uninstall manually but one malware cleaner, called AdwCleaner does a very good job of removing it, and many other common nasties. AdwCleaner is free and there is a link to the download at: http://goo.gl/CMnbgb.
